===============================================================================

Ocpp::Rails has been installed!

Next steps:

1. Run the migrations:

   rails db:migrate

2. The engine is mounted at /ocpp_admin

   Visit http://localhost:3000/ocpp_admin to access the dashboard

3. WebSocket endpoint for charge points:

   ws://localhost:3000/ocpp_admin/ocpp/:charge_point_id

4. Configure OCPP settings in config/initializers/ocpp_rails.rb

5. For ActionCable to work, ensure you have configured cable.yml:

   development:
     adapter: redis
     url: redis://localhost:6379/1

6. Start your Rails server with:

   rails server

For more information, visit: https://github.com/trahfo/ocpp-rails

===============================================================================
